.thefarside.com/2026/03/13/2</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 08:02:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-13 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/13/1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F9adc1640e4790137cd9d005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“The wench, you idiot! Bring me the wench!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/13/1</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 08:01:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-13 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/13/0</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fe0d03180e9ee0137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/13/0</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>